  "texts": [
    "IntroductionEmotions have a great impact on the basic cognitive process of people, but they are also very effective in the decision-making process as well [1].",
    "They play a crucial role in personal communication and many aspects of daily life [2].",
    "If emotions, which are an indispensable part of human life, can be fully recognized and predicted by computers, the advancement of the fields such as artificial intelligence, affective computing, or braincomputer interface will be considerably accelerated.",
    "Therefore, automatic human emotion recognition can be said to be a key technology for natural human-computer interaction (HCI) [3].HCI is an interdisciplinary field of study that deals with the design, evaluation, and application of interactive technology [4] and mainly refers to the interaction and relationship between humans and computers.",
    "From the past to the present, human interaction with computers has developed considerably and innovative interaction modalities have emerged."
